summary: An Ordinance transferring the sum of One Hundred Thirty-nine and 83/100 Dollars ($139.85) from Local Improvement District No. 1821, Fund, into the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of reimbursing said General Fund, for the deficiency in the Fixed Estimate of said district, for the improvement of Eighth Avenue, by constructing wood walks, as provided for in Ordinance No. 19013.
